reviewText: Its literally $50 cheaper to buy them seperately this price is a rip off.

I bought this is a surprise birthday gift for my husband. He's convinced that I could have gotten a better deal elsewhere, but I really wanted to buy seasons 1 - 13 in a pack, together, and I wanted to ensure that they'd be brand new. I didn't mind paying almost $300 for this set, as it was exactly how I expected it to be and it made my husband very happy.

I'm happy, too, knowing that what I bought was legitimate and not a foreign knock off or anythong like that. Lol. I always worry that I'll accidentally buy a DVD that's been ripped or something.

Anyway, everything about this was perfect. I am very pleased.
Season 1-6 are roughly $11 each($66), season 7-13 are roughly $20 each($140) = $206...Need to lower price.
I love the TV show all work and arrive on time.
